- @page_title = 'Unavailable Offer'

#main
  We're sorry but
  %span.name #{@offer.name}
  is no longer available. You can return to the previous page and refresh to view the latest offer list.
  %br
  %br

  - if @offer.item_type == 'App'
    %a{ :href => @destination_url }
      Or, click here to download #{@offer.name} anyway.

- content_for :page_styles do
  :plain
    #main {
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 115%;
    }
    .name {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #008810;
    }
